  "title": "School Management Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking For School Management Executive -</strong> (Assigned in School)<br /><strong>Contract Period:</strong> 19th March 2026 to 18 March 2027<br />Location: Jurong <br /><br /><strong>Personnel to be deployed at the following hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Mon to Thu: 9am to 6pm</li><li>Fri:  9am to 5:30pm</li><li>Service not required on Saturdays, Sundays and gazette public holidays.</li></ul><p><strong>The Scope of services:</strong></p><p><strong>Administrative duties include (Main):</strong>    </p><ul><li>Managing the student Admissions</li><li>Managing the registration website, database of students, informing students and parents of test date, preparation for selection interview, compile final list.</li><li>Assist VP/Year Heads in answering and writing replies to parents and students and also with Direct School Admission (DSA) /Joint Admission Exercise (JAE) appeal matters and student enrolments for returning Singaporean/International students.</li><li>Manage & Coordinate the Health (Mar to Apr) & dental screening registration for the students.</li><li>Assisting with Parent-Teacher Meetings (PTM) (Apr, June, July) </li><li>Liaising with internal & external departments.</li><li>Liaising with internal and external departments.</li><li>Perform other ad hoc duties regards to school events.</li></ul><p><strong>Administrative duties include (Others):</strong></p><ol><li>Cover reception duty from 4 p.m. to 6 p.m. daily </li><li>Verification of students with HR agencies </li><li>Printing of Name Cards. </li><li>Covering duty of reception duty and Student Services Centre (SSC) when required. </li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li>Candidate with minimum 2 years working experience in schools.</li><li>Qualification: A Degree Holder or equivalent</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Good team player and able to work in a fast-paced environment </li></ol><p><br />More details will be shared during the interview.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>ML Consulting Pte Ltd EA License No: 91C2939</strong></p><p><strong>ML Consulting Pte Ltd EA Personnel:  Aisha (R2512886)</strong></p>",
